{"tid":1225713,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[林鄭記者會] 睇緊直播，對啲記者提問有一點好想講","createTime":"2019-06-15T08:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T08:39:32.000Z","uid":7093,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"733a94f9fd9d64056ecb61afa83ff54e9d8850c9","tid":1225713,"uid":7093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"作為一個90後，我自細聽既學既<br />\n係「港人治港，高度自治」<br />\n除左軍事 同 外交<br />\n其他都係我地話事<br />\n<br />\n由幾時開始，大家好似接受左中國政府<br />\n係可以對其他事務有好大既話語權既呢？<br />\n<br />\n每一個記者提問，都係講緊<br />\n「覺唔覺對中央添煩添亂」<br />\n「有無得到中央支持？」<br />\n<br />\n呢條修例 無論點計都係local exercise <br />\n大家咁做根本係潛意識已經係度矮化自己<br />\n久而久之 就對呢件事習以為常<br />\n<br />\n呢個 唔係一個大問題咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e57b01229ae7104ecf3e247475f2018ee9662e1","tid":1225713,"uid":7093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:25:01.000Z","msg":"中央有最終話事權呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n暗啞底 同 擺上枱<br />\n差好遠下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc59c23a43cc454ae9e20e9a8594c93bc2f4756","tid":1225713,"uid":7093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:27:09.000Z","msg":"我淨係好擔心<br />\n我地下一代係呢個環境 呢個自我矮化既環境<br />\n已經唔知根據基本法同中英聯合聲明 我地根本就無需要理中央"},{"pid":"a1c7e9252ca197c66b4d629366c8668175475e57","tid":1225713,"uid":1425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"班記者真係好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1baf6d92194860e602af8da7cdfc7df109a741ad","tid":1225713,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:28:43.000Z","msg":"已經明面擺上枱左好耐 由97開始已經係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04208003cd659f43790ae9463109bdc1cd400ec3","tid":1225713,"uid":7093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote"